OL,3,CMandelson arrested over 'baseless
OL,4,Csuggestion' he was flight risk,
OL,5,Clawyers claim
OL,7,FLord Peter Mandelson's lawyers claim
OL,8,Fhis arrest was prompted by a "baseless
OL,9,Fsuggestion" that he was "planning to
OL,10,Fleave the country".
OL,12,FA spokesman for the law firm Mischon
OL,13,Fde Reya, on behalf of Mandelson, said:
OL,14,F"Peter Mandelson was arrested
OL,15,Fyesterday despite an agreement with
OL,16,Fthe police that he would attend an
OL,17,Finterview next month on a voluntary
OL,18,Fbasis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
