OL,3,CMandelson arrested over 'baseless
OL,4,Csuggestion' he was flight risk,
OL,5,Clawyers claim
OL,7,F"The arrest was prompted by a baseless
OL,8,Fsuggestion that he was planning to
OL,9,Fleave the country and take up
OL,10,Fpermanent residence abroad.
OL,12,F"There is absolutely no truth
OL,13,Fwhatsoever in any such suggestion.
OL,15,F"We have asked the MPS for the
OL,16,Fevidence relied upon to justify the
OL,17,Farrest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
