OL,3,CMandelson arrested over 'baseless
OL,4,Csuggestion' he was flight risk,
OL,5,Clawyers claim
OL,7,F"Peter Mandelson's overriding priority
OL,8,Fis to cooperate with the police
OL,9,Finvestigation, as he has done
OL,10,Fthroughout this process, and to clear
OL,11,Fhis name."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FLord Mandelson was released on bail in
OL,19,Fthe early hours of Tuesday after his
OL,20,Farrest on suspicion of misconduct in
OL,21,Fpublic office.
