OL,3,CMandelson arrested over 'baseless
OL,4,Csuggestion' he was flight risk,
OL,5,Clawyers claim
OL,7,FThe former Labour minister has been
OL,8,Faccused of passing highly sensitive
OL,9,Fgovernment information to paedophile
OL,10,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein during his
OL,11,Ftime as business secretary under
OL,12,Fformer prime minister Gordon Brown.
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was sacked as US
OL,15,Fambassador in September after Downing
OL,16,FStreet said fresh revelations about
OL,17,Fhis relationship with Epstein had
OL,18,Femerged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
