OL,3,CMandelson arrested over 'baseless
OL,4,Csuggestion' he was flight risk,
OL,5,Clawyers claim
OL,7,FHe resigned from the House of Lords
OL,8,Fearlier this month, following the
OL,9,Frelease of the so-called Epstein
OL,10,Ffiles; however, due to parliamentary
OL,11,Fprocedure, he retains his title.
OL,13,FLord Mandelson has not publicly
OL,14,Fcommented in recent weeks on the
OL,15,FEpstein files. According to the BBC,
OL,16,Fhe is understood to believe he has not
OL,17,Fcommitted any offence.
OL,19,FITV News has contacted the
OL,20,FMetropolitan Police for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
